4c3cd731e770c2ffa80e2","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學到D咩獨當一面技能</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起台 擺位 分餸 <br />\n最重要係點樣帶有笑容對住d西客"},{"pid":"4c5bdf2aa0e16c8e13541592cfe45aa9fa83db57","tid":47971,"uid":62115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最高試過幾多錢/hr<br />\n<br />\n我試過120$<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有經驗定熟人介紹？ 我自己有份正職返5日，想搵兩日出黎返下炒散，50幾60$都ok，但唔知點入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e358ca4ce1760598b943a9be0b0b9930c8b3b9a","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇啲咩有趣事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n客仔成日問橙汁係咪鮮榨橙汁 <br />\n用下腦都知係果汁先生倒出黎<br />\n但我會答係廢事煩"},{"pid":"e8b9ff7de7746a7b5a1d76b7ee4afd087786be94","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:40:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒左4年 咁家陣幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋試過一個月搵幾多錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n23歲 一個月chur盡有兩萬到"},{"pid":"fd5cc3eea5c6fc266b940a9aefdfda036b54f838","tid":47971,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:41:00.000Z","msg":"邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bdb6819d9c34da9164f1c2749501b0565cc541","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最高試過幾多錢/hr<br />\n<br />\n我試過120$<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有經驗定熟人介紹？ 我自己有份正職返5日，想搵兩日出黎返下炒散，50幾60$都ok，但唔知點入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網搵大把 依家根本求大過供<br />\n有手有腳就請"},{"pid":"a5a25129ad1b26899f419c96e02b61e8f39a7930","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師兄返開邊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6367438b79a6e21772e58f41b2cd07507d90faf","tid":47971,"uid":28194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:45:36.000Z","msg":"chur到盡先得2m幾 不如去做盤好過啦！<br />\n利申 22歲搵3萬幾"},{"pid":"75e1a5382b8155544f0b576294bd4ec5a0ee6a26","tid":47971,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>炒左4年 咁家陣幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋試過一個月搵幾多錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n23歲 一個月chur盡有兩萬到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果然年青有為<br />\n做左4年咁耐 暫時唔做唔會有啲後遺症<br />\n例如手震個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我之前都炒過一年散<br />\n做耐左個陣有一日放工發現有時會手震"},{"pid":"41d64f899df40b22fb43c7adc8182436ca172168","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:47:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>chur到盡先得2m幾 不如去做盤好過啦！<br />\n利申 22歲搵3萬幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每人chur既位都唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地盤日曬雨淋 酒店行行企企包三餐唔好？"},{"pid":"41887c47a8ee1b2b590fa31431b5e54d02de58f4","tid":47971,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>chur到盡先得2m幾 不如去做盤好過啦！<br />\n利申 22歲搵3萬幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChur盡一個禮拜返6日08-24<br />\n但基本上08-19個段時段都無乜野做<br />\n抹下銀器 行行企企 捱下眼訓<br />\n邊樣好做啲見仁見智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ce35e3153a7bcb3368b4ebb4a7b7a7aeabb8c5","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>炒左4年 咁家陣幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋試過一個月搵幾多錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n23歲 一個月chur盡有兩萬到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果然年青有為<br />\n做左4年咁耐 暫時唔做唔會有啲後遺症<br />\n例如手震個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我之前都炒過一年散<br />\n做耐左個陣有一日放工發現有時會手震</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n後遺症未有 但收工會腳酸 <br />\n你可能未識偷懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e84755fbdc2433cad998476c2918e33a3c8f5e5","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>chur到盡先得2m幾 不如去做盤好過啦！<br />\n利申 22歲搵3萬幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChur盡一個禮拜返6日08-24<br />\n但基本上08-19個段時段都無乜野做<br />\n抹下銀器 行行企企 捱下眼訓<br />\n邊樣好做啲見仁見智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nagger 眼訓係最辛苦"},{"pid":"0770ed2480bf750364f0c5592ccbd8452f909c05","tid":47971,"uid":28194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:52:52.000Z","msg":"咁又係 最緊要有工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e90a1dc350b5065433d9c110d3cd3a917e35edd","tid":47971,"uid":68182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:54:24.000Z","msg":"見冇乜人黎就爆下料先<br />\n<br />\n主人家比既利是係全部塞哂入經理袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aed454fbb05204c5f563883f1826af74d31eb5e","tid":47971,"uid":22312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:55:01.000Z","msg":"返開果間開始返到悶，想轉下環境，有咩好介紹"},{"pid":"804ef736417c0625f49ffcaf6952c77519cc9eae","tid":47971,"uid":6268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T17:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見冇乜人黎就爆下料先<br />\n<br />\n主人家比既利是係全部塞哂入經理袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}